name: Tejas Asbestos
overview:
Established in the year 1975, we, “Tejas Asbestos”, are a prominent entity of the industry specialized in trading an unmatched quality assortment of Asbestos Packing, Jointing Sheet, Insulation, Sealing and Ceramic Product.

Our products: Under this range, we offer Asbestos Yarn, Asbestos Cloth, Asbestos Woven Tape, Asbestos Lagging Rope, Asbestos PTFE Packing, Asbestos Grease & Graphite Packing and others. In addition to this, we also offer Asbestos Yarn, Asbestos Woven Cloth, Asbestos Woven Tape, Asbestos White Rope, Fibre Filled Lagging Rope and others.

Our Team; Recruited with us is a team of hardworking and enthusiastic professionals who act as a driving force for our organization and lead us to the path of growth and success.

Quality Assurance: Since our inception in this domain, we have been following quality approaches to bring forth an outstanding and peerless quality range of Asbestos Packing, Jointing Sheet, Insulation, Sealing and Ceramic Product to our valued clients.

Vendor Base: In order to cater to the varied market demands of patrons in an organized manner, we have associated our deed with credible vendors of the industry.

Client Satisfaction: Being a client centric organization, we lay our total dedication towards achieving the prerequisite requirements of patrons in an ordinal manner. Manufactured range that we come up with is precision engineered at the credible vendors base by making use of premium grade raw material in total conformity with the industry laid standards and guidelines.
